4. BE ſure you Waſte not the Subſtance committed to your Truſt: Yet, let not That be a Cloak for Covetouſneſs, (that
Grand Iniquity
                  ) but when there's cauſe for it, part with it freely, leſt through your Unfaithfulneſs therein, you be Rejected both of GOD and Good Men; for know, you are but Stewards of what you Poſſeſs, and for which you muſt be Accountable.
